channel.description: This is a sermon archive of Harvest Baptist Church in Lula, GA. Please note: it is the command of God that you find a local church to attend. Listening to this podcast in no way could ever replace the fellowship, care, and accountability a local church can provide! We pray these sermons serve to enrich your own walk with the Lord, alongside your faithful membership in a local church.
